  "title": "Tuition Teacher (Primary English & Mathematics)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company:</strong> ZHE Learning Centre<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time</p><p><u><strong>About the Role</strong></u></p><p>ZHE Learning Centre is seeking a <strong>dedicated and passionate Tuition Teacher</strong> specialising in <strong>Primary English and Mathematics</strong>. Candidates who can also teach <strong>Primary Science and/or Secondary-level subjects</strong> will have a strong advantage.</p><p>This role is ideal for educators who enjoy structured teaching, working closely with students, and contributing to a supportive academic environment.<br /></p><p><u><strong>Working Schedule</strong></u></p><ul><li><p><strong>Working Days:</strong> Tuesday to Saturday</p></li><li><p><strong>Off Days:</strong> Sunday & Monday</p></li><li><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM</p><ul><li><p>Includes <strong>1-hour lunch break</strong><br /></p></li></ul></li></ul><p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>Conduct <strong>Primary-level English and Mathematics</strong> lessons (group and/or small classes)</p></li><li><p>Prepare students for school assessments and national examinations through structured lessons</p></li><li><p>Provide clear explanations, guided practice, and constructive feedback to students</p></li><li><p>Monitor students’ progress and communicate observations when required</p></li><li><p>Prepare and adapt teaching materials to suit students’ learning needs</p></li><li><p><em>(Bonus)</em> Teach <strong>Primary Science</strong> and/or <strong>Secondary-level subjects</strong> when required<br /></p></li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>Diploma or A-Level qualification</strong>; Degree holders preferred</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in <strong>tuition or classroom teaching</strong> is highly advantageous</p></li><li><p>Strong command of spoken and written English</p></li><li><p>Patient, responsible, and able to manage students effectively</p></li><li><p>Comfortable teaching <strong>group classes</strong></p></li><li><p>Able to commit to the stated working schedule<br /></p></li></ul><p><u><strong>Why Join Us</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>Structured teaching environment with curriculum support</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to teach multiple levels and subjects</p></li><li><p>Collaborative and professional working culture</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities for high-performing educators<br /></p></li></ul><p><u><strong>How to Apply</strong></u></p><p>Interested applicants are invited to submit their <strong>resume</strong> and a brief <strong>introduction</strong> outlining their teaching experience to: 📧 danielngsy@zhelearning.com<br /><br />Subject: <em>Application for Tuition Teacher (Primary English & Math)</em></p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
